| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0546 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2d0e6d32-74e5-551d-b262-dc084bd1ee83"
